<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hopefully-adv">hopefully <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'həʊpfəli/    美 /'hoʊpfəli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>充满希望地； [句子副词] 有望：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He looked at her hopefully.
他满怀期待地看着她。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hopefully, I'll be able to stay at home for three weeks this time.
我这次有望在家待3周。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>If we leave right away, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (hopeful) we'll arrive on time.  （2013 浙江改）  </li>
<li>The boy looked at his father <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (满怀希望地) because he thought his father had brought him a present.  （2013 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. hopefully  2. hopefully  </p></div>